## Additional Information
Note that we also updated the `jakarta.ws.rs` import statements to match the Jakarta EE 9 or later namespace. This is because the Java API for RESTful Web Services (JAX-RS) is also part of the Jakarta EE platform.

In the `pom.xml` file, you will need to update the dependency for the Jakarta EE API to version 9 or later. For example:
```xml
<dependency>
    <groupId>jakarta.platform</groupId>
    <artifactId>jakarta.jakartaee-api</artifactId>
    <version>9.1.0</version>
    <scope>provided</scope>
</dependency>
```
You may also need to update other dependencies to match the Jakarta EE 9 or later versions.
